OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with clear spells.
OL,7,FRemaining dry overnight with any
OL,8,Flingering cloud clearing to give
OL,9,Flargely clear skies. Fresh southerly
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA dry and clear start to the
OL,13,Fday, but cloud building through the
OL,14,Fmorning. Remaining dry and mostly
OL,15,Fcloudy in the afternoon with some
OL,16,Fbright intervals. Fresh southerly
OL,17,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
