OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fon Monday with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fpossible. Bright spells Tuesday with
OL,8,Fshowers possible. Rain spreads
OL,9,Feastwards later Tuesday as winds
OL,10,Fstrengthen. Rain clearing to bright
OL,11,Fspells and showers Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
